message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you my product, which I know holds significant value for your business. While I can't disclose the exact details just yet, I can assure you it's worth at least $1 million to you.  I'm willing to part with it for a price of $950,000.  This is a great chance to secure a valuable asset at a competitive price.  Let me know your thoughts.
